data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF!  Rare opportunity to bring your boats, RVs & all the toys—42 Long Lake won’t last! This super private lot in Grande Oaks is ready for you to move right in. This meticulously maintained home features 3 bds, 2 bths, is the perfect size & features new paint, new carpet, granite counters, gas cooktop & fireplace, newer appliances, w/ an open floorplan all on 1 level. Meticulously maintained, enjoy the park-like setting of live oak trees that backs up to 25 acres of conservation land. Close to downtown Bluffton, Hardeeville, Savannah, 170 & May River Rd. Super low HOA, come see this beautiful community & why many love Grande Oaks!
